dialogue.speaker: Mother Nature
dialogue.text: I'M MOTHER NATURE, WISEGUY, AND I DON'T REMEMBER ASKING YOU TO SHUFFLE MY DEAD TWIGS AROUND.

dialogue.speaker: Pointy-Haired Boss
dialogue.text: UH... GOSH, I WAS JUST TRYING TO TIDY UP A BIT FOR SPRING...

dialogue.speaker: Pointy-Haired Boss
dialogue.text: ARE YOU SAYING YOU DON'T LIKE MY HOUSEKEEPING!!

dialogue.speaker: Mother Nature
dialogue.text: THAT'S IT. NO DINNER FOR YOU TONIGHT, AND I'M SENDING LOCUSTS TO EAT YOUR HOUSE.
